                <p>
                  The grievances received by the Department are forwarded to the concerned Ministries/Departments/State Governments/UTs, who are dealing with the substantive function linked with the grievance for redress under intimation to the complainant. The Department takes up about 1000 grievances every year depending upon the seriousness of the grievance and follows them regularly till their final disposal. This enables the Department to evaluate the effectiveness of the grievance redress machinery of the concerned government agency. <b>Department of Personnel &amp; Public Grievances</b> is the nodal agency to formulate policy guidelines for citizen-centric governance in the country.
                </p>
